name: Braixen
flavorText: When the twig is plucked from its tail, friction sets the twig alight. The flame is used to send signals to its allies.
Attack2Text: This attack does 60 damage for each Serena card in your discard pile.

name: Milotic
flavorText: Milotic has provided inspiration to many artists. It has even been referred to as the most beautiful Pokémon of all.
Attack1Text: This attack does 50 damage to 1 of your opponent's Pokémon. (Don't apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokémon.)
Attack2Text: Your opponent's Active Pokémon is now Asleep.

name: Flaaffy
flavorText: It stores electricity in its fluffy fleece. If it stores up too much, it will start to go bald in those patches.
Ability1Text: Once during your turn (before your attack), you may attach a Lightning Energy card from your discard pile to 1 of your Benched Pokémon.

name: Jynx
flavorText: In certain parts of Galar, Jynx was once feared and worshiped as the Queen of Ice.
Ability1Text: If this Pokémon is Knocked Out by damage from an attack from your opponent's Pokémon V, your opponent can't take any Prize cards for it.
Attack1Text: This attack does 10 more damage for each damage counter on your opponent's Active Pokémon.

name: Gardevoir
flavorText: It has the power to predict the future. Its power peaks when it is protecting its Trainer.
Ability1Text: You must discard a card from your hand in order to use this Ability. Once during your turn, you may draw 2 cards.

name: Malamar
flavorText: It's said that Malamar's hypnotic powers played a role in certain history-changing events.
Attack1Text: Reveal any number of Rapid Strike cards from your hand. This attack does 40 damage for each card you revealed in this way. Then, shuffle those cards into your deck.

name: Rockruff
flavorText: When it rubs the rocks on its neck against you, that's proof of its love for you. However, the rocks are sharp, so the gesture is quite painful!
Attack1Text: Flip a coin. If heads, discard an Energy from your opponent's Active Pokémon.

name: Passimian
flavorText: Passimian live in groups of about 20, with each member performing an assigned role. Through cooperation, the group survives.
Ability1Text: Your Rapid Strike Pokémon's attacks do 30 more damage to your opponent's Benched Pokémon V and Benched Pokémon-GX (before applying Weakness and Resistance). You can't apply more than 1 Throwing Coach Ability at a time.
Attack1Text: This attack does 20 damage to 1 of your opponent's Pokémon. (Don't apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokémon.)

name: Druddigon
flavorText: Druddigon are vicious and cunning. They take up residence in nests dug out by other Pokémon, treating the stolen nests as their own lairs.
Attack1Text: If any of your Pokémon were Knocked Out by damage from an attack from your opponent's Pokémon during their last turn, this attack does 120 more damage.

name: Smeargle
flavorText: It draws symbols with the fluid that oozes from the tip of its tail. Depending on the symbol, Smeargle fanatics will pay big money for them.
Attack1Text: Look at the top 5 cards of your deck. You may attach any number of basic Energy cards you find there to 1 of your Pokémon. Shuffle the other cards back into your deck.

name: Altaria
flavorText: As it flies in a calm and relaxed manner, Altaria performs a humming song that would enrapture any audience.
Attack1Text: Move all damage counters from 1 of your Benched Pokémon to your opponent's Active Pokémon.

name: Kricketune V
Ability1Text: Once during your turn, you may draw cards until you have 3 cards in your hand. If this Pokémon is in the Active Spot, you may draw cards until you have 4 cards in your hand instead. You can't use more than 1 Exciting Stage Ability each turn.
Attack1Text: Flip a coin. If heads, this attack does 80 more damage.

name: Serperior V
Attack1Text: Heal 30 damage from each Pokémon (both yours and your opponent's).

name: Blaziken VMAX
Attack1Text: During your opponent's next turn, the Defending Pokémon can't retreat.
Attack2Text: Choose up to 2 of your Benched Rapid Strike Pokémon and attach an Energy card from your discard pile to each of them.

name: Zeraora V
Attack1Text: If 1 of your other Rapid Strike Pokémon used an attack during your last turn, this attack also does 160 damage to 1 of your opponent's Benched Pokémon. (Don't apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokémon.)

name: Mawile V
Attack1Text: Flip a coin. If heads, discard an Energy from your opponent's Active Pokémon.
Attack2Text: Discard a random card from your opponent's hand.

name: Corviknight V
Attack1Text: During your opponent's next turn, the Defending Pokémon can't retreat.
Attack2Text: During your next turn, this Pokémon can't use Sky Hurricane.

name: Corviknight VMAX
Ability1Text: Prevent all effects of your opponent's Pokémon's Abilities done to this Pokémon.
Attack1Text: During your next turn, this Pokémon can't use G-Max Hurricane.

name: Rayquaza VMAX
Ability1Text: Once during your turn, you may discard your hand and draw 3 cards.
Attack1Text: You may discard any amount of basic Fire Energy or any amount of basic Lightning Energy from this Pokémon. This attack does 80 more damage for each card you discarded in this way.

name: Duraludon VMAX
Ability1Text: Prevent all damage done to this Pokémon by attacks from your opponent's Pokémon that have Special Energy attached.
Attack1Text: This attack's damage isn't affected by any effects on your opponent's Active Pokémon.

name: Blissey V
Ability1Text: Whenever you attach an Energy card from your hand to this Pokémon, remove all Special Conditions from it.
Attack1Text: This attack does 30 more damage for each Energy attached to this Pokémon. If you did any damage with this attack, you may attach up to 3 Energy cards from your discard pile to this Pokémon.

name: Rayquaza VMAX
Ability1Text: Once during your turn, you may discard your hand and draw 3 cards.
Attack1Text: You may discard any amount of basic Fire Energy or any amount of basic Lightning Energy from this Pokémon. This attack does 80 more damage for each card you discarded in this way.

name: Duraludon VMAX
Ability1Text: Prevent all damage done to this Pokémon by attacks from your opponent's Pokémon that have Special Energy attached.
Attack1Text: This attack's damage isn't affected by any effects on your opponent's Active Pokémon.
